        "text": "This indicator is not a signal generating indicator but rather one of many methods of generating Take Profit and Stop Loss levels.",
        "updated": 1622686933380
    },
    "paragraphs": [
        {
            "style": "Title",
            "text": "Info:",
            "updated": 1622481793076
        },
        {
            "style": "Text",
            "text": "The primary usage of this indicator is for the data found in the panel and to reference from your Trading System although it does come with a plotter in case you'd like to view the levels on your chart. You set the parameters at the data mining task => indicator bot instance as the default values (below) are arbitrary and based on relativeMovingAverage(trueRange).",
            "updated": 1622695020858
        },
        {
            "style": "Title",
            "text": "Default Values:",
            "updated": 1622481793076
        },
        {
            "style": "Text",
            "text": "periods = 15;  (for calculation of the ATR)",
            "updated": 1622694577540
        },
        {
            "style": "Text",
            "text": "take profit multiplier (of ATR) = 1;     (i.e.- 100% of ATR.)",
            "updated": 1622694767558
        },
        {
            "style": "Text",
            "text": "Stop Loss Multiplier (of ATR) = 1.5; (i.e.- 150% of ATR.)",
            "updated": 1622695076620
        },
        {
            "style": "Text",
            "text": "*Note* TP1 = 100% ; TP2 = 200% ; TP3 = 300%",
            "updated": 1622695096382
        },
        {
            "style": "Title",
            "text": "Parameters for Indicator Bot Instance:",
            "updated": 1622481793076
        },
        {
            "style": "Text",
            "text": "parameters at Indicator Bot Instance should look like this:",
            "updated": 1622694828029
        },
        {
            "style": "Text",
            "text": "{"
        },
        {
            "style": "Text",
            "text": "<b>\"periods\": value,",
            "updated": 1622694892884
        },
        {
            "style": "Text",
            "text": "\"tpMult\": value,"
        },
        {
            "style": "Text",
            "text": "\"slMult\": value"
        },
        {
            "style": "Text",
            "text": "</b>}"
